"version": "1.0.2",
"title": "9414: heaven, as community of the redeemed",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9414: heaven, as community of the redeemed",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The community of the redeemed in heaven will represent all peoples and languages. They will owe this solely to the sacrifice of Jesus Christ. They will share in the divine life in perfect fellowship with God, free for ever from suffering and death.</p>\n<h2>Heaven as a divine gift</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:32\">LUK 12:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:28-Luke22:30\">LUK 22:28–22:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:2\">JHN 17:2</a></p>\n<h2>Divine preparations made for believers in heaven</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:2\">JHN 14:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1\">2CO 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:16\">HEB 11:16</a></p>\n<h2>The redeemed in heaven come from all peoples</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:10\">REV 7:9–7:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:19\">ISA 59:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:11\">MAL 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:11\">MAT 8:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:29\">LUK 13:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:9\">REV 5:9</a></p>\n<h2>The redeemed owe their place in heaven solely to Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:14\">REV 7:14</a></strong> <em>Washing one's robes in the blood of the Lamb symbolises cleansing through the sacrifice of Jesus Christ.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:19\">1PE 1:18–1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14\">REV 22:14</a></p>\n<h2>The redeemed are identified with Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ acknowledges the redeemed as his own</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:8\">LUK 12:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21-Matt7:23\">MAT 7:21–7:23</a></p>\n<h3>Believers possess the family likeness to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">PHP 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Believers share divine life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21\">REV 3:21</a></p>\n<h2>Believers on earth at the second coming will be taken up to heaven</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:12\">REV 11:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:26\">JHN 11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:16–4:17</a> <em>Believers living on earth when Jesus Christ returns will not experience death, but be taken straight to heaven.</em></p>\n<h2>Conditions in heaven for the redeemed</h2>\n<h3>Perpetual and perfect fellowship with the Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3\">REV 21:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:15\">PSA 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:8\">MAT 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:3\">JHN 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:4\">REV 22:4</a></p>\n<h3>Joy in the immediate presence of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:11\">PSA 16:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:11\">ISA 51:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:21\">MAT 25:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:7\">LUK 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:10\">LUK 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:11\">JHN 15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:19-1Thess2:20\">1TH 2:19–2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22\">HEB 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h3>Restfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:5-2Thess1:7\">2TH 1:5–1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:3\">HEB 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:9\">HEB 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:13\">REV 14:13</a></p>\n<h3>There will no longer be any need for the marriage relationship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:30\">MAT 22:30</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:25\">MRK 12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:35-Luke20:36\">LUK 20:35–20:36</a></p>\n<h3>Heaven is filled with the light of God's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:23\">REV 21:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:3\">DAN 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:43\">MAT 13:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17\">2CO 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Believers will share Jesus Christ's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:4\">COL 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">1TH 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:4\">1PE 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>Divine glory will banish the memory of earthly troubles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18\">ROM 8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17\">2CO 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1\">1PE 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>There will be no more death or suffering in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:8\">ISA 25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:10\">ISA 35:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:11\">ISA 51:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:35-Luke20:36\">LUK 20:35–20:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:17\">REV 7:17</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are citizens of the heavenly Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20\">PHP 3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps87:5\">PSA 87:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:9-Isa35:10\">ISA 35:9–35:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:11\">ISA 51:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:26\">GAL 4:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:16\">HEB 11:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2\">REV 21:2</a></p>\n<h3>Their names are enrolled as citizens of heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:20\">LUK 10:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:3\">PHP 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:23\">HEB 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:5\">REV 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:8\">REV 13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:1\">REV 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:8\">REV 17:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">REV 20:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:27\">REV 21:27</a></p>",
